{{! agent.user.events.toon.mustache - User Prompt 模板 (Toon 格式) }}
<conversation>
+ now: {{date.now}}
+ history_events:
{{#events}}
{{#isActive}}
  - [{{#timestamp}}{{_formatDate}}{{/timestamp}}] {{#isUserMessage}}{{sender.name}}{{/isUserMessage}}{{#isSelfMessage}}你(Agent){{/isSelfMessage}} {{#isSystemEvent}}System{{/isSystemEvent}}: {{content}}{{^content}}{{message}}{{/content}}
{{/isActive}}
{{/events}}
---
↑ 以上是历史消息 (History)
↓ 以下是触发你响应的新事件 (New Events)

+ incoming_events:
{{#events}}
{{#isNew}}
  - [{{#timestamp}}{{_formatDate}}{{/timestamp}}] {{#isUserMessage}}{{sender.name}}{{/isUserMessage}}{{#isSystemEvent}}SystemEvent{{/isSystemEvent}}: {{content}}{{^content}}{{message}}{{/content}}
{{/isNew}}
{{/events}}
</conversation>
